Ale já se myla.

277
00:29:05,890 --> 00:29:07,620
Tos to tedy vzala hopem.

278
00:29:11,900 --> 00:29:15,360
Jak může holka takhle smrdět?

279
00:29:17,070 --> 00:29:21,270
